Protection of personal data - GDPR

   Billetweb collects data from attendees on behalf of event organizers.
   The organizers define the data to be collected, are the owners of the
   collected data and are responsible for the proper use of this data.
   Billetweb does not use or transfer this data in any way.
   Billetweb collects data about organizers who put on line their events
   in order to respond to legal constraints and to promote events.. The
   'organizer' data collected by Billetweb is neither sold nor sold to
   third parties.
   As part of the verification of the identity of the organizers imposed
   by Article L561-5 of the Monetary and Financial Code, Billetweb
   transmits the said documents to its banking partner Lemonway for the
   sole execution of the Payment Services.

   In accordance with the French law n ° 78-17 known as "Informatique et
   Libertés", the site has been declared to the CNIL under the receipt
   number 1759026 for the processing of your personal information. In
   accordance with this law, you have a right of access, rectification and
   deletion of your personal data. You can exercise this right from the
   contact.
